  "sentences": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In camp, we quite often were called out to do voluntary work.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "habitual_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 22695,
      "last_word_ms": 28945
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, if you went as a volunteer, then there was a chance of getting an extra soup.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 30335,
      "last_word_ms": 36705
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you didn't, then you got chased out and got treated quite badly.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 38075,
      "last_word_ms": 41255
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our room-- a roommate of mine, who was also the-- the head of our room, and whom I was very, very fond of, and myself very often all volunteered for work.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "habitual_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 44065,
      "last_word_ms": 57175
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got the soup and we usually gave it to the two kids whom we had in our room when we brought it back.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "habitual_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 57385,
      "last_word_ms": 63895
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This-- and one day we were called out and we had-- it was winter, and we had to bury-- well, it wasn't winter yet, but it was already icy and cold because it was in October, Or definitely by the end of September, it must have been.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 66335,
      "last_word_ms": 85295
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were-- were asked, and we had to bury-- dig-- dig a grave-- and I remember that the-- the ground was frozen-- dig a grave for the Commandant's dog.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 86755,
      "last_word_ms": 98905
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Commandant was standing there while we were doing it the whole time.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 100385,
      "last_word_ms": 103685
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, from that moment on I-- that I buried the Commandant's dog, whenever he saw me, he greeted me.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 105385,
      "last_word_ms": 113295
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now during my time in camp, I always said that I don't know German.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 114935,
      "last_word_ms": 119375
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I denied that I understand German, that I know German.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 120405,
      "last_word_ms": 123005
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I-- and-- and that's how it was accepted that I don't know German.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 124875,
      "last_word_ms": 131505
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, Willi was called away into-- to Buchenwald for a meeting for a couple of days.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 133035,
      "last_word_ms": 140525
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And during this couple of days, we did not get our bread.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 141485,
      "last_word_ms": 144075
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When Willi came back, we got our bread again.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "resolution",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 147095,
      "last_word_ms": 149955
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And a day or two later, I was standing next to two SS women, who were giggling and laughing and talking about it, how they sold the bread during those two days.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 151285,
      "last_word_ms": 164245
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "How they sold our bread and how they got away with it.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 164615,
      "last_word_ms": 167605
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know whether I gave myself away with my facial expression or what, but the one said, oh, it doesn't matter.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 168775,
      "last_word_ms": 175565
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She doesn't understand German, anyway.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reliving",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 175895,
      "last_word_ms": 177225
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they had an after thought and they went into my room and they asked one of my roommates, who was a pretty nasty individual, and said, do you-- does she really not understand German?",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Daily life (imprisonment)"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 178625,
      "last_word_ms": 192205
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, what are you talking of?",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_narration",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 192835,
      "last_word_ms": 194615
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's her mother tongue.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_narration",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 194755,
      "last_word_ms": 195385
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She only makes as if she doesn't understand German.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_narration",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 196025,
      "last_word_ms": 198475
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She speaks fluent German.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_narration",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 199395,
      "last_word_ms": 200285
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which wasn't a very nice thing to do, but anyway, she did it.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 201635,
      "last_word_ms": 205135
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the next day, they came, or a couple of days later, they came and they said that I must go to the appellplatz, to the zahlappell, there's a zahlappell.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 205685,
      "last_word_ms": 217005
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And only me, they called me out.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 218645,
      "last_word_ms": 220725
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I stood there and, at first, there was no one.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 221765,
      "last_word_ms": 224845
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then started-- many others started coming.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 225075,
      "last_word_ms": 227185
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we said, what's up?",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_narration",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 228315,
      "last_word_ms": 229355
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somebody said, oh, they are saying they are taking us to some lighter work into a paper factory.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_narration",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "mixed",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 229665,
      "last_word_ms": 234925
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- and I-- by that time, I was pretty weak already and pretty miserable and fed up and-- and of course, I would have loved to go into because I will tell about my work at that time.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Health",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 237135,
      "last_word_ms": 249715
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Would have loved to go to somewhere where the work would have been easier.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity",
        "Forced labor",
        "Health",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 250805,
      "last_word_ms": 254375
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so I stood there and then, when there were lots of us, I didn't know how many, the camp Commandant came with the camp doctor, Luciana Nissim, who was, by the way, an Italian, and who didn't speak Hungarian.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 256105,
      "last_word_ms": 273805
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she spoke French, and because she spoke French, we became great friends.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 273935,
      "last_word_ms": 277995
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are great friends up till today.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "present-day",
      "temporal_syntax": "present_reflection",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 278355,
      "last_word_ms": 279705
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was an absolutely lovely person.",
      "memory_type": "external",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "evaluation",
      "narrative_valence": "positive",
      "present_day_valence": "positive",
      "topics": [
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 281265,
      "last_word_ms": 282935
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what happened, we were-- and they counted us.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 284865,
      "last_word_ms": 290075
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Commandant counted us and we were 208.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 290515,
      "last_word_ms": 293155
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, that week, in the books of Luciana, people who came to her surgery she always had to write down.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "habitual_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 295895,
      "last_word_ms": 303645
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were 206, not 208.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "neutral",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 304055,
      "last_word_ms": 307885
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Commandant had been told that those who reported sick that week had to be taken away.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "orientation",
      "narrative_valence": "negative",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Health",
        "Captivity"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 309935,
      "last_word_ms": 316105
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there were only 206, not 208.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
      "narrative_valence": "neutral",
      "present_day_valence": "negative",
      "topics": [
        "Health"
      ],
      "first_word_ms": 317915,
      "last_word_ms": 319975
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he came and took me out and took another person out.",
      "memory_type": "internal",
      "content_domain": "wartime",
      "temporal_syntax": "strict_past",
      "narrative_structure": "complicating_action",
